Discussion: (Left this in as snacks being brought in is of major concern atm)

What do you think about having candy, chips and cookies this morning for breakfast? What do you think will happen? Do you think you will have more energy or not?

https://www.tinytap.com/activities/g3etm/play/healthy-vs-unhealthy

Play activity using above link: Use images to get students to differentiate between what is healthy and better for our bodies by getting them to put them into the 2 categories of healthy or unhealthy and possibly discuss an in between group of not so healthy but not so bad e.g. orange juice, smoothies, tacos…

See how students can discuss what happens?
Why do we need to eat healthy food?

After discussion:

BrainpopjrWatch :
Digestive System
Complete the easy quiz

Or Higher Level:
Digestive System | The Dr. Binocs Show | Learn Videos For Kids

