  values ('1ae193bc-c6e9-5afe-9a36-143c6ec3930d', 'c57154ed-1d22-5a84-bc5d-36f02a59c118', '00000000-0000-0000-0000-0000000005d3', 21, 'wed'::weekday, 'Writing', 'Writing:

Session 3 - Opinion Writing
Warm-up Discussion (10 minutes)
Ask:
"Do you choose food based on the brand?"
"What brands do you recognize and like?"
Make a whole-class list of popular brands.
Discuss: "Why do we like certain brands?" (e.g., taste, packaging, advertising, family choice).
    Opinion Writing Activity (25 minutes)
Students write a short opinion paragraph:
Opinion Statement: (e.g., "I think brand-name foods are better than non-branded foods.")
Two or Three Strong Reasons (e.g., "Branded foods taste better." / "They have fun packaging.")
Conclusion Restating Their Opinion
Provide sentence starters for support.
Sharing & Discussion (5 minutes)
A few students share their opinions.
Discuss different viewpoints.', '[]'::jsonb, '', '[]'::jsonb, '{}'::uuid[], 2)
