CCSS: 5.OA.A.1: Use parentheses, brackets, or braces in numerical expressions, and evaluate expressions with these symbols.

4 minutes- Review and Remember
8 minutes- Whole Class Preview and Performance Demonstration
10 minutes- Partner/Small Group Task
14 minutes- Individual Practice
10 minutes- Exit Ticket/Reflection/Direction', '[]'::jsonb, 'Note: 📐Unit 6: Math (Algebra, FDP, Coordinate Plane, Fractions)- Lessons Materials 📐Unit 6: Math (Algebra, FDP, Coordinate Plane, Fractions)- Online Resources

